          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "TiN targets with a thickness of about 280 mu-g/cm2",
                "were used. These TiN were prepared by evaporation on",
                "high-purity Cu foils with a thickness of about 20",
                "lm. The produced 26Al nuclei were implanted into the",
                "Cu foil.The Cu foils were tightly attached to a beam",
                "dump which was used as Faraday cup. Watercooling was",
                "used to decrease the target temperature, so that the",
                "targets could withstand 16O beam (16O4+ or 16O3+)",
                "intensities of 3 mu-A."
              ]
            }
          ],
